00:33:11,034 --> 00:33:13,008
Is that what you want? Do
you want a skinny person?

745
00:33:13,032 --> 00:33:16,034
No, but I would like to be
with a sane person, Kate.

746
00:33:18,021 --> 00:33:19,304
That is not nice.

747
00:33:19,339 --> 00:33:21,506
Yeah, well, maybe I'm a
little tired of being nice.

748
00:33:21,541 --> 00:33:23,008
Some stranger

749
