and you think I'm lying.

751
00:33:26,546 --> 00:33:27,617
Why is that?

752
00:33:27,642 --> 00:33:29,687
I don't... I don't
know. I have a problem.

753
00:33:29,712 --> 00:33:31,316
We all have problems, Kate.

754
00:33:31,351 --> 00:33:34,953
- Toby, all of my life...
