00:33:45,261 --> 00:33:47,265
She was terrible to me, Kate.

759
00:33:48,058 --> 00:33:49,465
Josie,

760
00:33:49,490 --> 00:33:52,938
this skinny, successful woman

761
00:33:52,972 --> 00:33:55,121
