gonna keep the job anyway.

784
00:35:19,690 --> 00:35:21,752
But you know who are good together?

785
00:35:23,993 --> 00:35:26,064
Matt Lauer and Savannah Guthrie?

786
00:35:26,089 --> 00:35:27,806
[quietly]: Yeah, duh.

787
00:35:27,861 --> 00:35:29,061
I love them.

788
00:35:29,096 --> 00:35:30,578
And I want them to be my family.

789
00:35:30,603 --> 00:35:32,231
And also us.

790
00:35:32,266 --> 00:35:34,159
We're pretty good together.

791
00:35:36,143 --> 00:35:39,159
