00:36:08,213 --> 00:36:09,990
I got the part.

801
00:36:10,141 --> 00:36:11,942
Yay, right? I think.

802
00:36:11,967 --> 00:36:13,668
Can you call me? Uh,
it's just, you know,

803
00:36:13,671 --> 00:36:15,806
you're-you're usually the one who...

804
00:36:15,840 --> 00:36:18,275
