some Snow White tonight, huh?

808
00:36:37,295 --> 00:36:38,996
[chuckles]

809
00:36:39,030 --> 00:36:40,297
Yeah.

810
00:36:42,934 --> 00:36:44,768
[sighs]

811
00:36:44,803 --> 00:36:47,268
I've offended you somehow.

812
00:36:47,739 --> 00:36:49,640
- No.
- No, I have.

813
00:36:57,063 --> 00:36:58,680
- You think I'm judging you.
- I...

814
00:36:58,711 --> 00:37:02,320
Because I'm in no position
to judge you whatsoever.

815
00:37:03,508 --> 00:37:07,244
But you need to know, if I
was in a position to judge you,

816
00:37:07,269 --> 00:37:08,745
you'd be getting a very high score.

817
00:37:08,770 --> 00:37:12,239
That story you told about helping to
bus little black kids in Pittsburgh.

818
00:37:12,274 --> 00:37:15,276
- That was '86, '87?
- Thereabout.

819
00:37:15,310 --> 00:37:18,475
So you were clean then?
Just... functional?

820
00:37:20,030 --> 00:37:22,047
Because you know what this
little black kid was doing?

821
00:37:22,071 --> 00:37:23,608
- I don't...
- I was a little boy,

822
00:37:23,633 --> 00:37:26,387
living in Bethel Park, Pennsylvania.

823
00:37:27,053 --> 00:37:29,590
Which is pretty much the
whitest place on Earth.

824
00:37:30,264 --> 00:37:32,639
I had this little notebook...

825
00:37:33,530 --> 00:37:36,239
and every time I met a new black person,

826
00:37:36,264 --> 00:37:39,522
I would put a mark in this notebook.

827
00:37:39,910 --> 00:37:44,535
And every time I met a black
man, I wondered if, somehow,

828
00:37:45,416 --> 00:37:47,715
if that man could possibly be my father.

829
00:37:47,751 --> 00:37:49,786
But I couldn't say that.

830
00:37:49,820 --> 00:37:51,891
You know, I couldn't say it out loud

831
00:37:51,916 --> 00:37:53,742
because I loved my father.

832
00:37:56,243 --> 00:37:57,927
My white father.

833
00:37:58,258 --> 00:37:59,758
And my white mother.

834
00:38:06,923 --> 00:38:10,306
I'm a strong, successful, black man.

835
00:38:10,977 --> 00:38:12,976
My wife and I give a lot of thought

836
00:38:13,010 --> 00:38:14,776
to how we raise our girls, believe that.

837
00:38:14,801 --> 00:38:16,284
- Yes.
- The fact that my daughter

838
00:38:16,309 --> 00:38:19,041
