and I will not apologize

845
00:38:36,220 --> 00:38:37,702
- for any of it.
- You shouldn't.

846
00:38:37,727 --> 00:38:39,094
- Because I don't.
- I should.

847
00:38:42,566 --> 00:38:43,866
Three weeks I've known you,

848
00:38:43,900 --> 00:38:45,359
and I still haven't said the words.

849
00:38:45,384 --> 00:38:47,719
- You don't have to say any...
- I'm sorry.

850
00:38:49,922 --> 00:38:52,484
I am so deeply sorry.

851
