I did everything wrong by you.

852
00:38:57,179 --> 00:38:59,230
And you've done everything right.

853
00:38:59,708 --> 00:39:02,913
You are doing everything right, son.

854
00:39:04,703 --> 00:39:08,373
♪

855
00:39:13,481 --> 00:39:15,082
Well, uh...

856
00:39:16,246 --> 00:39:18,666
Now, you wear whatever you
want on your walk tomorrow.

857
00:39:18,691 --> 00:39:21,473
Oh, I like my new flat
front khakis just fine.

858
00:39:21,498 --> 00:39:23,816
[both laugh]

859
00:39:24,168 --> 00:39:25,973
♪ I love my father,
