00:40:03,069 --> 00:40:05,155
You're kidding me, that's ridiculous.
All right, yeah, I'll be right there.

879
00:40:05,171 --> 00:40:06,771
We'll tell her what's up.

880
00:40:06,799 --> 00:40:09,167
- She's cute.
- RANDALL: Yeah, she is.

881
